{
  "stem": "16163.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's how we would get through that we got into-- not knowing we would get through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you were separated from your father?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Your father stayed--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were separated from my father, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother went, then, on my side, and we were-- were walked through a camp into some barracks, which turned out to be a sauna.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A sauna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, like what they call a sauna, like a cleansing place, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's where they shaved our heads and our body hair and took everything away from us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He must have been very surprised--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--that's for sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He must have been very surprised, but people were in such a daze what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we really didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't scared for my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very scared for my father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I didn't know when my mother went on the left side what would happen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then when they put my mother with me together, I said, all right.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least we are together, but what's going to happen to Papa?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, and like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was 50 years old at the time. 50?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had his 50th birthday still in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother-- I think I mentioned it to you before-- her very, very courageous woman.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this is not the last we saw of Mengele.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had an experience with him right before the war ended.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we got-- well, we got into Auschwitz, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we-- later on, we were selected to a labor camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we landed up at [NON-ENGLISH], subsidiary of Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- which it was called Marzdorf.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
